  <summary date="2020-02-05T13:00:32Z" status="Introduced in Senate">K9s for Veterans Therapy Act

This bill requires the Department of Veterans Affairs to implement a pilot program to assess the effectiveness of addressing post-deployment mental health and post-traumatic stress disorder through a method where veterans train service dogs for veterans with disabilities.</summary>
